  "description_snippet": "VULNERABILITY DETAILS\n\n# Late Load Elimination\n\nInside the TurboShaft Late Load Elimination Phase, the `LateLoadEliminationAnalyzer` does not handle `Call` nodes carefully enough.\nThe `CopyFastSmiOrObjectElements` Builtin is handled as a special case, leading to no invalidation of memory loads apart"
